# What are <u>Pedigree Charts</u>?
Pedigree Charts are used to **show patterns of inheritance** in a family **tree** 

**![An image of a Pedigree Chart|600](https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/5Q20Xakqun-WYLzs_rSubQ8_1Px1auqGDDrhN7T6UY6NcaWu_9ouzKZ4p-phkwJdJS1Ww8K47t7lm992pjLSaJ5dNR5kUtJJko28fRYO01RheH4MVRS5njpLBWu9-jynNDDRSkqbjMDUZkgsOnd8noDgHQ=s2048)**

## Reading Pedigree Charts

- **Females are circles, males are squares**
- A marriage is a line between two shapes
- Offspring are shown by drawing a branched line down from a marriage
- A **shaded shape means the person has the trait**
